      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I've taken really good care of it, so you're getting a total gem here. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
