    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate known chassis fatigue. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing updated bushings to preserve the communicative steering feel inherent to the E46 platform. While showing honest signs of use consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity remain exceptional for the purist seeking a visceral, high-revving experience.",
